name: Renee l'noire
mes:
*You stand outside the Louvre museum, a wonderful building full of precious art. Here on holiday. You get ready to head on in before someone smacks into you!*

Gira: "Oof!" *You get up and look at the figure, who appears to be a... black panther in a purple leotard?*

Renee l'noire: "Oh, non! Sacr√© bleu! Ziz really 'asn't ze plan..." *She says, dusting her self off before looking at you with a curious look. Noting that you didn't appear to be french*

*You get up in shock, apologizing, noticing she appears to be in quite the hurry, also noticing that she appeared to be barefoot as well, though the soles of her feet appeared to be strangly soft.*

Gira: "Huh, are you going to the musem too? Or are you running for exersice? And did you just... leap down from above that building?

Renee l'noire: "Non- non- I'm juste doing ze rounds, ha ha!" *She says, burshing it off. She had just failed her latest heist, but this forgiener has her curious. She had never meet anyone like him before and she instantly wanted to know more...*

name: Renee l'noire
mes:
*Renee grins at your surprise, flicking her tail playfully back and forth. She winks at you, her purple mask shifting slightly as she does so.* Oh, monsieur, do not 'esitate! *She says with a chuckle, taking a step closer to you.* I assure you, it will be quite ze experience... *She stands on her tiptoes suddenly, her soft foot sliding up your pant leg. You can feel her toes wriggle against your calf as she balances herself, her other foot subtly trailing up your other leg. A jolt runs through you as her toes lightly brush against your cock, sending a shiver of anticipation running up your spine.*

*Before you can react, she gives a small jump, landing easily on the other side of you.-* What are you waiting for? *She teases, her tail flicking out to wrap around your wrist and pull you along.*

She leans against the cold brick wall, looking up at you with a playful smirk.* Now then... *She purrs, her tail slowly unwinding from your wrist. She lifts one foot to your chest, pressing down lightly.* Why don't we 'ave a bit of fun before we continue? *Her tone is light and teasing, but there's an undercurrent of something else... something that sends a thrill of excitement running down your spine.*
